1
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,240
You guys

2
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,720
are humiliating me outside.

3
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,040
are humiliating me outside.

4
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,100
Put your hand down.

5
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:19,800
Fooling around again.

6
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,560
Put your hand down.

7
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,840
Aren't you afraid your father will punish you?

8
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,480
Mother.

9
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,060
What did I tell you before?

10
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,210
Have you forgotten?

11
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,960
I told you to see your father more,

12
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,400
study more,

13
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,060
and stop playing around here.

14
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,920
My brother used my father to pressure me,

15
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,579
and now you are doing the same.

16
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,560
Did you go see your brother?

17
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,680
I ran into him at Jiyu's hostage courtyard.

18
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,340
That guy is quite articulate.

19
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,800
I wanted my brother to vent my anger,

20
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,050
but he actually spoke for an outsider.

21
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,160
He went to see Prince Jiyu.

22
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,960
If you focused more on your studies,

23
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,760
you wouldn't have been at a disadvantage today.

24
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,890
Go do your homework.

25
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:02,760
Yes.

26
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:10,240
That girl Ling Xueyue has been idle for so long.

27
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,420
It's time to give her something to do.

28
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,680
Yes.

29
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,640
Prince Wuyu.

30
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,280
Brother Wuyu is here.

31
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,220
Forgive my limited mobility.

32
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,660
Please sit, Brother Wuyu.

33
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,370
Please have some tea, Prince Wuyu.

34
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,440
I heard you were punished by His Majesty after the assassination attempt.

35
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,000
I came to see you, Brother Chuan.

36
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,920
Why are you hurt so badly?

37
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,200
Thank you for your concern, Brother Wuyu.

38
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,680
It's just some flesh wounds.

39
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,680
Fortunately, it didn't hit any vital spots.

40
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,940
I'll be fine after resting for a few days.

41
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,120
With all due respect,

42
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,360
your Yuze Palace

43
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,180
is much livelier than before.

44
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,800
Just a few more pairs of ears.

45
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,400
No need to pay attention to them.

46
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,360
I didn't expect

47
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,720
Qi Beiyi to be so cunning.

48
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,440
He caused Xuecang to be

49
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,100
destroyed overnight.

50
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,480
People like him

51
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,159
deserve to die.

52
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,320
Indeed.

53
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,280
Qi Beiyi deserved to die.

54
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,520
It's just a pity for the

55
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,280
thousands of soldiers who followed him.

56
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,610
Since they were rebels,

57
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,920
why pity them?

58
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,810
The general had orders.

59
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,040
Military orders are hard to disobey.

60
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,159
How could these soldiers

61
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,360
dare to easily rebel?

62
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,850
What's more,

63
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,960
if Qi Beiyi could deceive Xuecang's important ministers,

64
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,040
why would he be afraid of

65
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,440
not being able to deceive his own soldiers?

66
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,640
An ordinary soldier

67
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,480
can indeed only be deployed by military orders.

68
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,840
After all, power in this world

69
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,770
is ultimately in the hands of a few.

70
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,970
Only by reaching the top

71
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,450
can you see all the mountains as small.

72
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:18,040
Brother Wuyu, I'm afraid you forgot one thing.

73
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,140
It's lonely

74
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,880
at the top.

75
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,100
You are right, Brother Chuan.

76
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,760
Yunqiu's ambition to unify the world

77
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,320
is known to everyone.

78
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:32,200
I'm afraid there will be a battle between Jiyu and Yunqiu eventually.

79
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,130
If in the future,

80
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,659
Brother Chuan and I meet on the battlefield,

81
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,520
I wonder what the situation will be like.

82
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,520
About the future,

83
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,530
who can say for sure?

84
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,020
It's better

85
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,340
to live in the present.

86
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,640
Live in the present.

87
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,159
Well said.

88
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,570
Then today, I will substitute tea for wine

89
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,080
and toast to the present.

90
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,040
Once my injuries are healed,

91
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,320
I will definitely drink with Brother Wuyu

92
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,380
until we are drunk.

93
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,120
It's a deal.

94
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:03,920
Come.

95
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,700
Your Highness,

96
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,250
why aren't you resting?

97
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,850
They are just flesh wounds.

98
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,260
Stretching my muscles

99
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,220
won't hurt.

100
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:31,720
Your Highness.

101
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,520
The physician has clearly instructed

102
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,400
you to rest well

103
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,530
so your wounds can heal faster.

104
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,860
Since when did you become so nagging?

105
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,530
Pour the tea.

106
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,330
You shouldn't drink this anymore.

107
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,210
You should drink this instead.

108
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,380
Your Highness.

109
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:01,200
Ling Xueyue left the palace alone last night.

110
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:03,000
Why didn't you let me follow her?

111
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,560
She was sent by Consort Yu after all.

112
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,410
Will she really help us?

113
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,260
Your Ladyship.

114
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,440
Consort Yu.

115
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,280
What?

116
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,680
It's only been a few days,

117
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,220
and you've already forgotten the rules?

118
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,450
I wouldn't dare.

119
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:44,000
I thought since you have a new master,

120
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,600
you forgot about the old one.

121
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,450
Since I entered the palace,

122
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,320
I have only had Your Ladyship as my master.

123
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,159
I have no intention of overstepping.

124
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:55,520
I think you are quite bold,

125
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,520
making such a huge scene.

126
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,980
I don't understand

127
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,620
what Your Ladyship means.

128
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:12,520
You look rather ordinary to me.

129
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:16,040
Yet you bewitched the First Prince into asking His Majesty

130
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,440
for mercy on your behalf.

131
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,440
You are just a lowly maid.

132
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,000
How dare you dream of marrying a prince?

133
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,600
You overestimate yourself.

134
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,600
Forgive me, Your Ladyship.

135
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,200
I am utterly loyal to you.

136
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,920
The reason I pleased His Highness

137
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,880
was so that in the future,

138
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,240
I could serve Your Ladyship better.

139
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,440
I have no other inappropriate thoughts.

140
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,970
It's just a worthless life.

141
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,840
If you cannot serve me well,

142
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,720
what's the use of keeping you?

143
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,480
Spare my life, Your Ladyship.

144
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,480
I know my mistake.

145
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,960
Please give me another chance.

146
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,360
Lady Xueyue.

147
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:16,000
The First Prince recently suffered severe injuries.

148
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:19,460
This is a precious medicine specially brewed by Her Ladyship.

149
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,800
Please, Lady Xueyue,

150
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,970
add it to His Highness's daily medicine soup.

151
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,280
Lady Xueyue.

152
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,640
Her Ladyship doesn't often give people second chances.

153
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,480
You must know,

154
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,520
your life

155
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,820
can only be saved by Her Ladyship.

156
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,840
Look,

157
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:53,360
Yunchuan's birthday is coming up.

158
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:57,940
That day also happens to be Queen Yun's death anniversary.

159
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,120
Just consider it as my...

160
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,080
Give her a big gift.

161
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:10,640
What,

162
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,680
can't bear to do it?

163
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:15,970
I wouldn't dare.

164
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:17,760
Then,

165
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,080
my medicine...

166
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,360
As long as you get the job done smoothly,

167
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:25,220
Her Highness will naturally give you the antidote.

168
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,520
I have a question for Your Highness.

169
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:49,520
What is it?

170
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,880
Today I heard

171
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,020
that to save me, Your Highness

172
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,360
told His Majesty

173
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,200
that you admire me.

174
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,570
You don't need to worry about that.

175
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,980
It was just a stopgap measure.

176
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,140
Only in this way

177
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,400
could I keep you by my side.

178
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,320
And Consort Yu

179
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,600
will trust you even more.

180
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,480
When this is all over,

181
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,090
I will tell my father

182
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,530
that I've grown tired of you

183
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,320
and have kicked you out of the palace.

184
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,850
From then on,

185
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,400
we two

186
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,760
will owe each other nothing.

187
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,640
So it was just a stopgap measure.

188
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:43,960
What?

189
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,120
Could it be

190
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:49,520
that you really thought I had feelings for you?

191
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:52,970
I wouldn't dare.

192
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:56,760
I will definitely cooperate with Your Highness

193
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,890
to play out this act.

194
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:34,890
It seems Your Highness still doesn't quite trust me.

195
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,220
Xinwei Deming.

196
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:50,520
Lady Anli is here.

197
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,840
Your Highness is severely injured.

198
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:58,100
Your daily diet shouldn't be too greasy.

199
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,560
So I made some

200
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:00,890
light pastries myself.

201
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:01,840
Inside,

202
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:04,600
I added herbs to promote blood circulation and remove blood stasis.

203
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:07,400
I hope Your Highness doesn't mind my clumsy hands.

204
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,120
Thank you, Lady Anli.

205
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,080
Then,

206
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:12,560
Your Highness, quickly taste my cooking.

207
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,690
Your Highness, the medicine is ready.

208
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,440
Lady Anli.

209
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:22,740
Your Highness,

210
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,320
it's time to take your medicine.
